---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify leading-relaxed">
    Technical Support Specialist L2 with strong Linux and infrastructure background.
    Experienced in enterprise monitoring (Zabbix), incident management, root cause analysis,
    and automation of support processes. Proven ability to handle escalated technical tickets
    under pressure, investigate complex issues, and improve operational efficiency.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Professional Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="System Administrator (Monitoring & Infrastructure)"
      subtitle="Kyndryl (IBM) | Wroclaw, Poland | June 2022 – Present"
    >
      Led monitoring platform migration from DataDog, Nagios, Netcool and ScienceLogic to Zabbix.
      Optimized alerting logic and thresholds. Handled escalated incidents in ServiceNOW (ITIL).
      Developed Python and Bash scripts for log analysis and automation, significantly reducing manual work.
    </TimeLineElement>

    <TimeLineElement
      title="Platoon Leader - Chief of Radio Relay Station"
      subtitle="Armed Forces of Ukraine | October 2019 – April 2021"
    >
      Led mission-critical communications operations in high-pressure environment.
      Ensured reliable infrastructure and secure connectivity under stress.
      Managed team coordination and operational risk assessment.
    </TimeLineElement>

    <TimeLineElement
      title="LMS System Administrator & Digital Learning Manager"
      subtitle="Hedgehog (USA company) | Ukraine | September 2021 – December 2021"
    >
      Maintained 99% platform uptime. Handled technical troubleshooting and system administration
      for internal users and learning platform.
    </TimeLineElement>

    <TimeLineElement
      title="System Administrator"
      subtitle="Poltava District Clinic Center | Ukraine | July 2019 – May 2021"
    >
      Administered Linux and Windows infrastructure, managed backups, network configuration
      and resolved daily technical issues for users.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Master's in International Marketing and Management"
      subtitle="University of Management and Economics ISM (BI Norwegian Business School) | 2013 – 2017"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Master's in Economical Cybernetics"
      subtitle="National University 'Yuri Kondratyuk Poltava Polytechnic' | 2007 – 2012"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Key Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-3 columns-2 mx-6 mb-10">
    <li>Zabbix Administration & Alert Optimization</li>
    <li>Linux Systems Administration (RHEL / Ubuntu)</li>
    <li>Incident Management & Root Cause Analysis</li>
    <li>ServiceNOW & ITIL Processes</li>
    <li>Python & Bash Scripting</li>
    <li>Log Analysis & Troubleshooting</li>
    <li>Monitoring Platform Migration</li>
    <li>High-Pressure Environment Operations</li>
    <li>API & Webhook Basic Troubleshooting</li>
    <li>Automation of Support Tasks</li>
    <li>English (B2)</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li>Red Hat Certified System Administrator (RHCSA EX200)</li>
    <li>Microsoft Azure Administrator (AZ-104)</li>
    <li>ITIL 4: Introduction to Service Management</li>
    <li>Cisco CCNA</li>
    <li>Microsoft Azure Fundamentals (AZ-900)</li>
    <li>LPI Linux Essentials</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
